pliers (ADMM) to replace the original problem with an equivalent sequence\nof sub-problems that are amendable to convex decompositions, leading to a\nhighly parallel algorithm. We demonstrate the performance on real data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2016 17:27:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-11-17"}
