igin. Further improvements to the\ntreatment of the gas-physical processes regulating the star formation histories\nof galaxies are clearly necessary to resolve these problems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Jan 2016 21:00:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
